data.description: Newly CERTIFIED PRE-INSPECTED BY ORGOVA HOME INSPECTIONS!!! Assumable mortgage for VA buyers @ 4.25%!!! Also USDA eligible!!!    Welcome home to this well maintained, like-new 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home that is just one year old! Step inside and instantly feel at home in this thoughtfully designed residence, that perfectly accommodates a modern lifestyle.    The open floor plan effortlessly connects the spacious living area, dining room, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, stunning quartz countertops, and a large island that serves as a perfect hub for meal prep and casual dining.    This home features spacious bedrooms, each offering ample living and storage space. The large master suite provides a private haven complete with an ensuite bathroom and oversized walk in closet. Indulge in the luxury of a large walk-in shower, quartz countertops, and double vanity sinks.    Note that this home offers solar panels, a significant contribution to energy efficiency that will noticeably reduce your utility costs. Please note that the solar panels are leased and will be transferred to the buyer at closing (at a cost of $44 per month).    Located centrally with easy access to Tampa, Orlando, Legoland, and the world-famous Disney attractions, this home offers the perfect balance of convenience and excitement. Embrace the endless possibilities that await you and make this your new home base for creating unforgettable experiences.    Schedule a private showing today and explore the potential of this extraordinary property! All measurements are approximate and should be verified by the buyer. Please be aware that the property has various steps and may have uneven surfaces, so we kindly ask you to watch your step.
